  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Residence Bernerhof Apartments are on a self-catered basis. Bed &amp; Breakfast is available for a supplement.</p>
<p>If you have upgraded to Bed &amp; Breakfast you can enjoy a buffet breakfast each morning including a selection of cheeses, cold cuts, muesli, cereals and up to ten different homemade jams and jellies.</p>
<p>If you dont feel like cooking, head to the Hotel Bernerhofs' own restaurant the 'Taverne' which offers typical Swiss specialties including fondue, röstis, raclette and homestyle dishes, as well as international cuisine. Pay locally.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
