  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studio Apartments </strong>sleep one to two people in a double bed. These 20m² apartments are ideal for single guests or couples looking for a comfortable space to relax after a day on the slopes.</p>
<p><strong>Larger Studio Apartments </strong>sleep two to three people. These 25m² apartments have a double bed and a single bed, making them a good option for small families. </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Nespresso machine</li>
<li>Equipped kitchenette with oven, fridge, kettle</li>
<li>Bath with showerhead attachment or shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Cots are available for CHF30 per stay</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that these apartments are dog friendly.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
